Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: THIS happened\Nwhile we were gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: Wow! Those are\Nall the places we went
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when we left to\Nsave Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! There's that HORRID town\Nwhere we were almost sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirates! They were\Npretty awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,er.. once they decided not\Nto throw us overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mt. Aris! Ooo, Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know we made seashell\Nnecklaces for AAALLL-LLLL the seaponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that unicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who attacked\NCanterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tempest. I invited her\Nto come to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but she wanted to\Nspread the word
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Storm\NKing's defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and share what she\Nlearned about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all think that's\Nwhy the map grew?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship quests\Nbeyond Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had quite enough\Nlife-threatening adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How many friendship quests do\Nyou think we need to go on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,before we have to\Nexpand the throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do it all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to knock this wall\Ndown, get some paint--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I mean the world is\Nfilled with so many different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,creatures who know nothing\Nabout friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We need help if we're gonna\Nteach them all about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity: Perhaps. But\Nwhere does one go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn about\Nfriendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! They can all go here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're gonna\Nopen a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: I think a\NSchool of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is a wonderful\Nidea, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help in\Nany way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a few questions:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What time should\Nschool start each day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It really de-\NWhat's the ideal\Nlength for class?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you test regularly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well that's--\NWhat about\Nclass projects?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a ver--\NAssigned seating?\NOpen seating?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that too\Nunstructured?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight! You\Nwere my star pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone knows how to\Nrun a school, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a big difference\Nbetween attending a school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and running one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like there's a\Nrulebook to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA guidebook\Nis very specific
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to\Nrun a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA? I've never\Nheard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I have\Nheard of that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, you've never\Nrun a school before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Equestria Education\NAssociation is a board
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of learned ponies that oversee\Nevery school in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even YOUR school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're...YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a Princess can\Ndo whatever she likes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to shaping\Nyoung pony minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA ensures that whether\Nit's unicorns studying magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,pegasi learning weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or earth ponies\Nresearching agriculture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all schools are held to\Nthe same high standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll need to\Napprove your plan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,before you can\Nmove forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have a\Npresentation to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff. After everything we've been\Nthrough, how hard can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go with\Nreally hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Hello. My name is--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight\NSparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Chancellor Neighsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria owes you\Na great debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But Princess or no, we expect\Nyou to do things by...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Book!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll\Nfind my curriculum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,meets all your\Nrequirements, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And can we trust you to follow\Nthrough with this plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you leave the\Nschool unattended
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to gallop off on your\N... adventures?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My journey beyond Equestria\Nshowed me first hoof
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that the threats out there\Nare greater than we imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If we want to keep\Nour land safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and create a\Nfriendlier tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to teach the magic\Nof friendship far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A school for ponies to learn\Nhow to protect themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, more like respecting\Ndifferences and communicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA concurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony should be prepared\Nto defend our way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if your work is in order,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,provisional EEA\Napproval is granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will need to observe your\Nschool up and running
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,before it can be\Nfully accredited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please, join us for\NFriends and Family Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a perfect time\Nto see our progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash: It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,TOO MUCH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity: Ah! You think so!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I had hoped dressing the part\Nwould help me{\i1} feel{\i0} the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This! Us! Teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna think\NI'm an egghead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the students are gonna\NLOVE my confetti cannon class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be.. a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Hello there.\NI'm your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't enjoy it,\Nthat's OK, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about this\Nschool just feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See? If Twilight\Nisn't stressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got nothing\Nto worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're SURE you\Nwant US to be teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In.. classrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA is VERY clear on how\Nschools should be run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a HUGE\Nresponsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need you all to do\Nthis by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That means no cannons\Nin class, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awwwwww! Not even\Na teeny cannon..?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not some big adventure\Nagainst the forces of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But this could be the\Nmost important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we've ever done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run a school\Nof Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,without my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you\Ncan, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Professor\NEgghead. I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHHH! FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL!\NSO MANY NEW PONIES!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,About that. ONE thing\NI forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not JUST ponies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Students certainly\Ntraveled from far and wide
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to attend our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia helped me\Nreach out to all the kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, friendship\Nis something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that needs to be shared\Nwith every...creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the School\Nof Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your headmare,\NTwilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow Guidance\NCounselor Starlight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to sign in and get your\Nclass assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can show you\Nyour living quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sandbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a student\Nhere, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I just figured I'd\Nrandomly stand here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and see how many ponies\Nwould walk into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry male voice: GALLUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Gruff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Flew all the way\Nfrom Griffonstone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to introduce Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilda told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Thought you'd\Nbe... cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gruff male voice: PONIES!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This Yona Yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She come to pony school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak can't wait\Nto meet ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell ALL about\NYakyakistan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I show you around\Nbefore you destroy the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But dragons are\Nbetter than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as Dragon Lord,\NI'm ordering you to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Spike! Come meet Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Great to see you, Ember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Which one is Smolder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocellus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we\Ntalk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in your\Nown form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the polite\Nthing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.. She's shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know ponies\Ncould turn into...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies can turn into\Nchangelings!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But changelings\Ncan turn into ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. That's confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am General Seaspray of Her\NMajesty Queen Novo's navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to introduce the\Nqueen's niece, Silverstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spent most of my life in\Na coral reef under water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a seapony. But now I'm\Na hippogriff, long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways... WOW!\NIS THAT A YAK!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for\Nsupporting the grand opening
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll all join us for\NFriends and Family Day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the amazing progress\Nyour students are making!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like school's\Nin session!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The School of Friendship! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ First Day of Class! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Will we fail or{\i0}\N{\i1} will we pass? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Students come from{\i0}\N{\i1} far and wide! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Brand new friends{\i0}\N{\i1} here by our side! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Take a breath, look{\i0}\N{\i1} around, it's amazing ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I can't believe that it's real ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Students galore{\i0}\N{\i1} New ideas to explore ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't contain the{\i0}\N{\i1} excitement I feel! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't mess up{\i0}\N{\i1} Can't afford a mistake now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Think success!{\i0}\N{\i1} Keep it firmly in sight ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Make sure to do things{\i0}\N{\i1} by the book! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Make sure to do it{\i0}\N{\i1} all right! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The School of Friendship! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Must get to class! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Will we fail or{\i0}\N{\i1} will we pass? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Students learning{\i0}\N{\i1} from the best! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Taking notes to pass{\i0}\N{\i1} the test! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Wait hold on! Not like that,{\i0}\N{\i1} just a second. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'm not sure if that{\i0}\N{\i1} method's approved. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Let me take a look. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Yup! Right here in the book ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Come on!{\i0}\N{\i1} We just got in the groove! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't mess up{\i0}\N{\i1} Can't afford a mistake now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We are shaping young minds{\i0}\N{\i1} to ignite! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Do it like it says{\i0}\N{\i1} in the book now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Make sure you're{\i0}\N{\i1} doing it right! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's not an equation{\i0}\N{\i1} on how to have fun! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The students look bored now{\i0}\N{\i1} Oh, what have I done! ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't teach bein' honest{\i0}\N{\i1} Not sure what to do! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'm quite certain I'm lost ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ NONE OF US HAS A CLUE ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The School of Friendship ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Another Class ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Wish it were more{\i0}\N{\i1} of a blast ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Thought this school{\i0}\N{\i1} would be more fun ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't wait for our{\i0}\N{\i1} classes to be done ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't mess up{\i0}\N{\i1} Can't afford a mistake now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ No way to have fun ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Oh, what have I done! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Bored with this class ♪{\i0}\N{\i1} ♪ Think success. Keep it firmly in sight ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Wish that we could{\i0}\N{\i1} leave en masse ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We don't have a clue ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Listen to this one request ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Make things fun{\i0}\N{\i1} we're really stressed ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Make sure to do things{\i0}\N{\i1} by the book nooowwww... ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can we tell her this{\i0}\N{\i1} thing is a mess? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what boring is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,THESE ponies are the\Nheroes of Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, "these ponies" saved\Nall of us from The Storm King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How? By boring him\Ninto surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teachers are a little\Ndifferent than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Pony school\Nwaste of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,YAK school teach how\Nto braid Yak hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,BRAIDING YAK HAIR IS BEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything in Yakyakistan\Nthat isn't the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Wait. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No claws, no\Nwings, no fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it exactly\Nyou're proud of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, cool it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to harsh Yona's\Nlove for her heritage. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we not being sweet and\Nfriendly enough for you, pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sarcasm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you weren't\Nbeing sweet or nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe dragons and griffons are\Njust too tough for friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just not nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you calling\Nnasty, klutz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, break it up!\NBREAK. IT. UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going\Non here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a friendly discussion\Nabout the magic of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony--I\Nmean--everyONE--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,go to your next class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't\Nbelieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fights breaking out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're supposed to\Nbe learnin' friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Things definitely aren't\Ngoing as "by the book"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as Twilight planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we're\Nterrible teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Face it. This school\Nisn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: Fights breaking out\Nin the hallways!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't look like\Nthat! Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are getting off to a\Nrougher start than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you and what have you\Ndone with Twilight Sparkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Every school in Equestria\Nfollows these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we do\Ntoo, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,try something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA will be\Nhere this afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for Friends and Family Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to see a school that\Nfollows their guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if those guidelines\Naren't working..?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, we have to try\Nharder and make sure they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Another morning, another\Nchance to inspire our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Professor Dash's\Nclass is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...\Nskipping, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly\Nwhat we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But Friends and\NFamily Day--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--is AFTER class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax! This is just a\Nquick... mental health break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll\Ntag along too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure you don't\Nget into.. trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy: This\Nway, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! What are\Nyou all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't classes\Nthat way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A generosity field\Ntrip, dahhhling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the students\Nto the laaake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at our\Ndivine reflections.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I take back everything\NI said about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...What did you\Nsay about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure sticking to the\Nbook is going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends can\Nhandle anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have these problems\Nturned around before we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Neighsay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And you\Nseem unprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Problems? Ha!\NOf course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait to\Nshow you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[nervous laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why griffons\Nbreathe fire when we get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They do NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffons just full of hot air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And yaks are actually\Ngood at jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are dragons\Ngood at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's up for a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you in\Nclass teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my\Nstudents are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, gone...somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing a loyalty lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just going to\Ngrab, uh ... this pencil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Which I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,cause.. I'm the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, Chancellor,\Nwe have other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just...---\NLet's follow the... professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite curious about\Nthis "lesson in loyalty."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Twilight: Of course,{\i0}\N{\i1} we want to instill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} a sense of loyalty{\i0}\N{\i1} towards others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We encourage acts of{\i0}\N{\i1} generosity and kindness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Figured we shouldn't be the\Nonly ones enjoying the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,AGH! YAKS NOT BEST AT FLYING!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} An appreciation for{\i0}\N{\i1} the value of laughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,FLYING IS BEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are officially the weirdest\Nthing I've seen so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Ocellus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you be weirder\Nthan a flying yak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,OH!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,... and to always be\Nhonest in any situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honesty is imperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, are we\Ngoing in circles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better head to the lake\Nfor Friends and Family Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure all the students and\Nfaculty will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SCHOOL IS UNDER ATTACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, maybe skipping class\Nwasn't the best idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How DARE you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This act of aggression\Nagainst ponies--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry,\NChancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We clearly had some students\Nget a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,THOSE are students?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you said you were\Nopening this school
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To defend ponies from\Ndangerous creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who don't have our best\Ninterests at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My school teaches for all\Nof us to work together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,through friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you know\Nthese.. creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,won't take what they've learned\Nhere and use it against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship isn't\Njust for ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicorn think yaks\Nno need friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe yaks no\Nneed pony school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then perhaps you\Nshould return to your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your kind!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Novo will want\Nto hear of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This place seemed\Nlame anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We know not everypony\Nsees us the way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia helped me\Nreach out to all the kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When she hears you closed\Nthe school because--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you failed to\Nmeet the EEA's standards?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Irresponsible teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Students skipping class!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Endangering ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your school is a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps if you had higher\Nstandards for who was admitted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this could have been avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of the EEA,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am shutting\Nthis school DOWN.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
